m content for plain text search\n- Include code block content\n- Handle empty file list\n- Valid JSON output\n\n#### **Wave 3 (Depend on Wave 2) - 16 Tests**\n\n**sitemap.test.ts** (8 tests):\n- **Dependencies**: taxonomy, rss-feed\n- Generate `sitemap.xml`\n- Include all `.html` pages from ctx.output\n- Include taxonomy tag pages (`tags/*.html`)\n- Include `feed.xml` if present\n- Build full URLs using baseUrl from config\n- Valid XML structure: `<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>`, `<urlset>`, `<url>`, `<loc>`\n\n**dev-server.test.ts** (8 tests):\n- **Dependencies**: asset-pipeline, search-index\n- Store `dev-server-config` in ctx.data\n- Config structure: `{port, routes: [{path, handler}], assetPaths, searchIndexPath}`\n- Default port: 3000\n- Extract asset paths from asset-manifest\n- Create routes for assets (handler: \"asset\") and content (handler: \"static\")\n- Include search-index.json path\n- Handle missing asset-pipeline data gracefully\n\n### 7. PACKAGE.JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-ssg-toolkit\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"SSG Toolkit benchmark - static site generator with DAG plugin system\",\n  \"main\": \"dist/core/index.js\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/ tests/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.1\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.9.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.1.9\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@types/express\": \"^5.0.6\",\n    \"@types/marked\": \"^5.0.2\",\n    \"express\": \"^5.2.1\",\n    \"marked\": \"^17.0.2\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Key Dependencies:**\n- `marked` - For markdown parsing (used by markdown-ext plugin)\n- `express` - For dev server support\n- TypeScript 5.9.3 with strict mode enabled\n\n### 8. TSCONFIG.JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"target\": \